snippet.title: Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Siege – Shadow Legacy: Gameplay and Tips
snippet.description:
Zero, the new Operator from Operation Shadow Legacy, is going to whip you into shape... Discover the brand new Chalet map, the new capabilities of Zero and everything that the season is bringing to the game.
